eventText: Carla asks when can she receive the app for testing? Sambhaji said on Monday, 19Feb.
A new testflight version with latest data is sent to Carla.
Carla informs Shrinath and Piyush that she is not able to see the Rheumatologie app.
Shrinath invites Carla one more time to test the app.
Carla has now downloaded the app and is testing now.
Carla checks the app and sends back the feedback.
Sambhaji sends the decision to change the copyright year from 2017 to 2018.
Carla approves the app and requests to send the screenshot PDF of whole app. Also send the app to external testers on testflight.
Check the installation status by external testers and reply back to Carla.
Testflight version for both iOS and Android sent to Carla and external testers.
Screenshot PDF is sent to Carla.
Carla informs that Mrs Stehlin has not received the invitation to test the app.
Shrinath and Piyush sends the Android apk again. Also requests to send the device type.
Carla sends back the feedback that some of the links are not working in the Android app.
Carla has sent more feedbacks for Rheumatologie app.
Carla will send the screenshots to client related to links.
Gaurav follows up with Carla for changes and approvals
Carla has approved the Rheumatologie app.
App is approved by Apple. Sambhaji tells Shrinath, Kiran to release the app.
